---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout page_title="About Me">
  <main>
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>
      Based in the Dallas-Fort Worth area, I'm a passionate photographer dedicated to capturing 
      extraordinary moments through my lens. Photography is my way of preserving beauty, emotion, 
      and fleeting moments that tell unique stories.
    </p>

    <h2>My Services</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service">
        <h3>Sports Photography</h3>
        <p>Capturing the intensity and emotion of athletic moments, from touchdowns to game-winning shots.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <h3>Event Photography</h3>
        <p>Documenting special occasions, corporate events, and celebrations with attention to detail.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <h3>Portrait Photography</h3>
        <p>Creating stunning portraits that showcase personality, whether individual, family, or professional.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <h3>Landscape Photography</h3>
        <p>Capturing breathtaking natural and urban landscapes with dramatic lighting and composition.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>My Approach</h2>
    <p>
      From dynamic landscapes to detailed portraits, I aim to create images that
      evoke emotion and tell a story. Whether it's finding the perfect light,
      experimenting with creative angles, or editing to enhance the final
      composition, I love every part of the process.
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond the technical side, photography allows me to connect with people
      and places in a meaningful way. Every photo I take is a reflection of my
      perspective and a moment I want to preserve and share.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-container">
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Ready to book? Contact me today!</a>
      <a href="/gallery" class="cta-button secondary">View my portfolio</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-sm) 0;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .service {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .cta-container {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cta-button {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--secondary);
  }

  .cta-button.secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }

  .cta-button.secondary:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-container {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
